<lb ed="I" n="0093a02"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead><title>僧演造像記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan><cb:div>
<pb n="0094a" xml:id="I01.0038.0094a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0094a01"/><p cb:type="pre" xml:id="pI01p0094a0101">郭世貴一心供養
<lb ed="I" n="0094a02"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0094a03"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0094a04"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0094a05"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0094a06"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0094a07"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0094a08"/>清信駱花嬰
<lb ed="I" n="0094a09"/>一心供養佛時</p></cb:div><cb:div>
<pb n="0094b" xml:id="I01.0038.0094b" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0094b01"/><p cb:type="pre" xml:id="pI01p0094b0101">夫大覺神<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0094001" n="0094001"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0094001" n="0094001"/><anchor xml:id="beg0094001" n="0094001"/>遷<anchor xml:id="end0094001"/>。非經像無以表其
<lb ed="I" n="0094b02"/>真。益世閏時。<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0094002" n="0094002"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0094002" n="0094002"/><anchor xml:id="beg0094002" n="0094002"/>憑<anchor xml:id="end0094002"/>形<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0094003" n="0094003"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0094003" n="0094003"/><anchor xml:id="beg0094003" n="0094003"/>質<anchor xml:id="end0094003"/>如<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0094004" n="0094004"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0094004" n="0094004"/><anchor xml:id="beg0094004" n="0094004"/>取<anchor xml:id="end0094004"/>利。然
<lb ed="I" n="0094b03"/>僧<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0094005" n="0094005"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0094005" n="0094005"/><anchor xml:id="beg0094005" n="0094005"/>演<anchor xml:id="end0094005"/>減割衣鉢之資。造石像壹
<lb ed="I" n="0094b04"/>區。金像三區。<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0094006" n="0094006"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0094006" n="0094006"/><anchor xml:id="beg0094006" n="0094006"/>浮<anchor xml:id="end0094006"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0094007" n="0094007"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0094007" n="0094007"/><anchor xml:id="beg0094007" n="0094007"/>圖<anchor xml:id="end0094007"/>三級。大般<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0094008" n="0094008"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0094008" n="0094008"/><anchor xml:id="beg0094008" n="0094008"/>涅<anchor xml:id="end0094008"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0094b05"/>槃經<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0094009" n="0094009"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0094009" n="0094009"/><anchor xml:id="beg0094009" n="0094009"/>兩<anchor xml:id="end0094009"/>部。雜經三百<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">品</unclear>。供養僧
<lb ed="I" n="0094b06"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">卅</unclear>人。上為　<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0094010" n="0094010"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0094010" n="0094010"/><anchor xml:id="beg0094010" n="0094010"/>國<anchor xml:id="end0094010"/>主。百僚。師徒<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0094011" n="0094011"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0094011" n="0094011"/><anchor xml:id="beg0094011" n="0094011"/>所<anchor xml:id="end0094011"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0094b07"/>生。法界之<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0094012" n="0094012"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0094012" n="0094012"/><anchor xml:id="beg0094012" n="0094012"/>類<anchor xml:id="end0094012"/>。咸同正覺。
<lb ed="I" n="0094b08"/>大統四年。<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0094013" n="0094013"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0094013" n="0094013"/><anchor xml:id="beg0094013" n="0094013"/>歲<anchor xml:id="end0094013"/>次<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0094014" n="0094014"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0094014" n="0094014"/><anchor xml:id="beg0094014" n="0094014"/>戊<anchor xml:id="end0094014"/>午。七月十五
<lb ed="I" n="0094b09"/>日。比丘僧<anchor xml:id="beg_1" type="star"/>演<anchor xml:id="end_1"/>敬造供養。</p></cb:div><cb:div>
<pb n="0094c" xml:id="I01.0038.0094c" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0094c01"/><p cb:type="pre" xml:id="pI01p0094c0101">
<lb ed="I" n="0094c02"/>比丘道暈　比丘僧暢　比丘僧通
<lb ed="I" n="0094c03"/>比丘僧<anchor xml:id="beg_2" type="star"/>演<anchor xml:id="end_2"/>　比丘僧普　比丘惠云
<lb ed="I" n="0094c04"/>比丘法迴　比丘僧敬　比丘僧轁
<lb ed="I" n="0094c05"/>比丘僧端　比丘法豪　比丘道賢
<lb ed="I" n="0094c06"/>比丘僧曠　比丘僧云　比丘僧和
<lb ed="I" n="0094c07"/>比丘惠遵　比丘僧濟
<lb ed="I" n="0094c08"/>比丘道洸　比丘僧玉
<lb ed="I" n="0094c09"/>比丘法崇　比丘僧均　比丘法和</p></cb:div><cb:div>
<pb n="0094d" xml:id="I01.0038.0094d" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0094d01"/><p cb:type="pre" xml:id="pI01p0094d0101">
<lb ed="I" n="0094d02"/>董大女供養佛清信士萬□
<lb ed="I" n="0094d03"/>董當供養佛時
<lb ed="I" n="0094d04"/>董僧供養佛時
<lb ed="I" n="0094d05"/>董歡供養佛時清信女趙季寄供養
<lb ed="I" n="0094d06"/>董□樂供養佛清信女李□□供養
<lb ed="I" n="0094d07"/>姚舍欣供養佛
<lb ed="I" n="0094d08"/>殄難將軍郭穆供養佛清信女李□妙供養
<lb ed="I" n="0094d09"/>伏波將軍任歡供養佛</p></cb:div></cb:div>
</body>
